{
  "stem": "3097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If I fight, and I get killed, at least I will take somebody with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew that the Germans have plans for me that I will not survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started to plan already to do something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They selected a group of strong, small boys, but very strong physically.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody knew who was strong, because we did a lot of things-- they are lifting stuff, and the [INAUDIBLE], you see, who was strong, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To work in the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Gestapo was at the other end of the city by the big park and the lagoon in our city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our function was to lift up and carry heavy furniture in the Gestapo building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the attic, they had a warehouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they collected-- there were no Jews anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They collected things from the Poles, who were all destroyed or sent to Auschwitz, OK?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, I go to warehouse where the Poles-- and I moved some coal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a gun laying down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took this gun, put it right here in my crotch, you see, attached with the strings, and took it, OK?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I took it to the-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans did not--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--search us, because they are afraid to get sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it so happened, I took this gun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I put it in some grease from a machine, you see, in a little box and buried it in the ground outside the barrack, OK?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then once, I go on the roof, and there I saw two of officers' boots-- high boots-- open here, cut open here like from a dead body.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was, on the attic, they had lime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A little bit of wood, but mostly was lime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The attic was made out of lime there on the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
